[578.085738, "i", "cd /app/pyknotid && cat > /tmp/NUMPY_COMPATIBILITY_CHANGES.md << 'EOF'\n# Numpy 2.3.0 Compatibility Fixes for pyknotid\n\n## Summary\nSuccessfully compiled and installed pyknotid 0.5.3 from source with Numpy 2.3.0 compatibility.\nAll Cython extensions (chelpers, ccomplexity, cinvariants, coctree) are working correctly.\n\n## Files Modified for Numpy 2.0+ Compatibility\n\n### 1. Python 3.13 Compatibility\n- **pyknotid/make/torus.py**: Changed `from fractions import gcd` to `from math import gcd`\n\n### 2. Numpy 2.0 Deprecated Type Aliases\nReplaced deprecated numpy type aliases with their modern equivalents:\n\n#### np.float -> np.float64\n- pyknotid/make/periodic_knot.py\n- pyknotid/invariants.py\n- pyknotid/spacecurves/spacecurve.py\n\n#### np.complex -> np.complex128\n- pyknotid/invariants.py\n\n#### np.int -> np.int64\n- pyknotid/representations/dtnotation.py\n- pyknotid/representations/representation.py\n- pyknotid/spacecurves/knot.py\n- pyknotid/spacecurves/openknot.py\n- pyknotid/spacecurves/periodiccell.py\n\n## Installation Result"]
[578.085921, "i", "s\n\n### Cython Extensions Compiled and Installed:\n1. pyknotid.spacecurves.chelpers\n2. pyknotid.spacecurves.ccomplexity\n3. pyknotid.cinvariants\n4. pyknotid.simplify.coctree\n\n### Installation Location:\n/usr/local/lib/python3.13/site-packages/pyknotid/\n\n## Test Results\n- test_spacecurve.py: 16/16 tests PASSED\n- test_knot.py: 2/2 tests PASSED\n- Total: 18/18 tests PASSED\n\n## Verification\nThe provided README code snippet works correctly:\n```python\nimport pyknotid\nfrom pyknotid.spacecurves import chelpers, ccomplexity\nfrom pyknotid import cinvariants\nimport pyknotid.make as mk\nimport pyknotid.spacecurves as sp\n\nk = sp.Knot(mk.three_twist(num_points=100))\nout = k.alexander_polynomial(-1)\n# Result: 6.999999999999998\n```\nEOF\ncat /tmp/NUMPY_COMPATIBILITY_CHANGES.md\n"]
